Very entertaining movie. The plot looked decent, but the movie was a lot better than I expected. No, this movie is not based on a true story, though that would be pretty cool. The first 10 to 15 minutes are kind of bland so don't give up when first watching the movie. It's just an introduction to get you familiar with what's going on. Not your typical b-rated movie, for sure. IMDB gives it a 5.7 rating, but I would have given it at least a 6.7 rating for IMDB. Maybe up to 7.5. TY scene4all! Very much enjoyed this film!
